reviewText: I thought it was some of his recent work wouldn't that funny at all had i seen this first wouldn't know how funny he really is cause i would never watch anymore of his works

Not only did I not receive the dvd but it was a cd of Rev Timothy Wright. Such a major disappointment considering I was going to use the dvd for a fellowship at church. I did contact the seller and was refunded but still who sends out a mess like that? This is not Craiglist or Ebay. I just think the seller should stop having this item online especially if they are not selling what is presented. I should have known better after I got it because the case looked fake. Never again!

This is very funny...they really know how to do comedy down south. Clean for the entire family and christian-based so the jokes have a lot of meaning...

I still tell some of the jokes to my friends and family. Very funny!
